class.name: CATMSHCustomHighlight
class.abstract: Interface representing a pre-highlight and highlight of a finite element entity.

constructor.abstract: Creates an object which defines custom hiligth method an associated data.

method.name: HighlightEdge
method.abstract: Defines the default hiligth behaviour for the edge of finite element.

method.name: HighlightElement
method.abstract: Defines the default hiligth behaviour of finite element.

method.name: HighlightFace
method.abstract: Defines the default hiligth behaviour for the face of finite element.

method.name: HighlightNode
method.abstract: Defines the default hiligth behaviour for a node.

typedef.abstract: Customized method which be called for the highlight.
